reviewText: film meanders with no intention of gettign anywhere, not poorly executed but whats the point

Australian genre films are so underrated! This movie is so awesome. If the budget is twice the amount of money it took in at the box office you can bet your in for a treat and Midnite Spares doesn't disappoint. 1983 was a hell of a year!
Purchased this for my Brother as I shop for his movies on amazon cuz he doesn't have internet. He really likes older muscle car movies and he really liked this one.
Bruce Spence is apparently pretty good, cause he is different in about any movie I can find with him in it.  "A piece of history" for sure.  I was glad to get this movie in my library.
